message.entry: Caching the same {0} object twice is not supported.
Incorrect number of input arguments. Each parameter name must be followed by a corresponding value.

Cannot use ObjectCacher's cache function to cache this object. The object needs to either\n1. Inherit from matlabshared.testmeas.internal.mixins.CacheEnabler, or\n2. Define an ObjectType property with a string value.
